history.created_by: RUN |1 DAYTONA_VERSION=0.52.1 /bin/sh -c apk update && apk add --no-cache curl openssh-client bash &&     echo "daytona:x:1000:1000:Daytona:/home/daytona:/bin/bash" >> /etc/passwd &&     echo "daytona:x:1000:" >> /etc/group &&     mkdir -p /home/daytona && chown 1000:1000 /home/daytona # buildkit
RUN |1 DAYTONA_VERSION=0.52.1 /bin/sh -c chmod +x /install.sh && DAYTONA_VERSION=${DAYTONA_VERSION} /install.sh && rm /install.sh # buildkit
RUN |1 DAYTONA_VERSION=0.52.1 /bin/sh -c chmod +x /darwin/get-config.sh && chmod +x /linux/get-config.sh && chmod +x /windows/get-config.cmd # buildkit
